ists/confidence-man">Confidence Man</a>和 Altered Images 也有表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nottinghams-splendour-festival-cancelled-leaving-organisers-frustrated-3576355">诺丁汉辉煌音乐节被取消，让组织者“沮丧”的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
